Title: WWW: Work Weather Wife
Actors: Harpreet Sandhu, Reema Nagra, Harrajan Sandhu, Simran Sandhu
Plot: Vick tricks his way into fragile family of Dimple and CJ. Film outlines major community issue of Honour Killings. CJ being a worker class doesn't have time for daily routine around the house and Vick outsmarts CJ on a scam.
